It's been a week since I set up my personal blogging site and wrote my first article, and now I'm writing my second one! This is definitely a good sign and I'm feeling positive for the future of this blog thing.

Anyways, let's now talk about the main topic of this article: setting up automated publishing of this blog site using Github Actions, why I need one and how I did it.

## The Aim for Maximum Convenience